'''& Pictures''' is a [[Hindi language|Hindi]] satellite movie channel in India based in [[Mumbai]]. The channel is owned by the popular [[Zee Entertainment Enterprises]] which is a part of [[Essel Group]].<ref>{{cite web|author=Our Bureau |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/companies/zee-to-launch-movie-channel-under-new-brand-pictures/article5003965.ece |title=Zee to launch movie channel under new brand ‘& pictures’ &#124; Business Line |publisher=Thehindubusinessline.com |date=2013-08-08 |accessdate=2013-09-01}}</ref> It is the first channel of [[Zee Entertainment Enterprises]] under the new brand '''&'''.<ref>{{cite web|author=Nandini Raghavendra |url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2013-08-01/news/40963081_1_satellite-rights-zee-entertainment-film-rights |title=Zee buys satellite rights of Chennai Express for its upcoming channel '& Pictures' - Economic Times |publisher=Articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com |date= |accessdate=2013-09-01}}</ref> It also shows Hollywood movies.

