'''Korea Ferrous Metals Export & Import Corporation''' is a [[steel]] company based in [[Pyongyang]], [[North Korea]].<ref name="Steel 2012">{{cite web|title=Korea Ferrous Metals Export and Import Corp.|url=http://business.highbeam.com/company-profiles/info/1352868/korea-ferrous-metals-export-and-import-corp|publisher=High Beam Research|accessdate=11 October 2012}}</ref> The company imports coal, fuel and some components as raw materials.{{Citation needed|date=October 2012}} It produces many steel products for export and domestic use.<ref name="Steel 2012"/>

Products include steel [[Plate (metal)|plates]], [[hot rolling|hot-rolled]] steel [[sheet metal|sheets]], [[pig iron]], [[bar (material)|square steel]], [[round (material)|round steel]], seamless steel [[pipe (material)|pipes]], [[wire]] and [[Electrical cable|cable]] and [[ferrosilicon]].{{Citation needed|date=October 2012}}

Its offices are located at Pothonggang-dong 1, [[Potonggang-guyok]], Pyongyang, North Korea.

